44 枚透镜多方位打散出光，防眩不刺眼。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img alt="图片 1" height="679" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/11/88622b66-1881-4c03-8463-7bf4aab31b7e.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="赠米家液晶小黑板：小米米家立式学习灯 1590 元新低（上市 2299 元）" width="629" /></p><p>此外，该产品配备无线蓝牙遥控器，双击可开启专注模式，并支持无级调光、管理用眼时间；可通过米家 App 设置与其他智能设备的联动，<span class="accentTextColor">打造包括“人来灯亮”在内的自动化智能场景</span>，支持小爱音箱语音控制开光灯。</p><p>该产品采用 90° 可旋转 + 探出式灯头，配备 10kg 重、0.8cm 厚的底座，支持前后 15° 防倾倒，通过国标和欧盟 6° 防倾倒测试。</p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/KGXlqbl" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="250" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/63ec2d08-9ae9-450f-b214-0441a225d0c2.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="赠米家液晶小黑板：小米米家立式学习灯 1590 元新低（上市 2299 元）" width="250" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">小米米家立式学习灯</span></span><span class="card-abstract">定制全光谱灯珠</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 1590.95 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p>2024 年 11.11 大促全网好价合集：<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fcontentlist%3Fapi%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnapi.ithome.com%252Fapi%252Ftopmenu%252Fgetmenufeeds%252F166%252F0%252Fnone%252F0%26title%3D2024%25E5%258F%258C11%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BF%2583%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E9%2580%2589%26mode%3D0" target="_blank" title="点此查看">点此查看</a></p><p><span class="font-color-red"><strong>京东无门槛红包&nbsp;</strong></span>至高 11111 元：<a href="https://u.jd.com/CaQySbH" target="_blank" title="点此抽今日红包"><strong>点此抽今日红包</strong></a></p><p><span class="font-color-orangered"><strong>天猫无门槛红包&nbsp;</strong></span>至高 24888 元：<strong><a href="https://s.click.taobao.com/w26hFPt" target="_blank">点此抽今日红包</a></strong></p><p><span class="font-color-purple"><strong>唯品会无门槛红包</strong></span> 至高1111元：<a href="https://t.vip.com/VbMVne" target="_blank"><s